Invocation Name: super sweat
des: Super Sweat is an Alexa skill that aims to provide the user with the ability to create a custom HIIT workout specified to their need. In this skill you can customise the time you would like to workout for, the length of time each exercise will last, the time in-between each exercise, as well as the portion of your body you would like to workout, and the music you would like to listen too. Now you know a little more about the skill, would you like to continue?
